# IDE - Visual Studio Code
.vscode/
*.code-workspace

# IDE - CLion / IntelliJ with C/C++ plugin
.idea/
cmake-build-*/

# IDE - Xcode workspace user data
**/xcuserdata/
**/xcshareddata/
